"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-gabby-thomas-healthcare-career-olympic-gold-paris\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Of course Jennifer Randall is thrilled that her daughter, Gabby Thomas, will head to Paris later this month to compete in her second Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999417923, \"rank\": 5.823537400570362e-11, \"text\": \"Gabby Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 85, \"end\": 90, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9969016885049966, \"rank\": 0.003107940863609571, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her daughter\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 56}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Olympic Games\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Young Gabby was always faster than her peers; her grade school soccer team strategy was to boot the ball over everyone else\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s head and let Gabby chase it down.\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Young Gabby\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 159}, {\"ngram\": \"her peers\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 192}, {\"ngram\": \"her grade school soccer team strategy\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 266}, {\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Randall was the one who told her she could do this, who when Gabby was 11 or 12 proclaimed that she would be an Olympic runner.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic runner\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe rolled her eyes at me and sashayed out of the room,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Randall says.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"her eyes\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But a dozen years later, there Thomas was,earning a bronze medal in Tokyoin the 200 meters, and a silver in the 4x100, while Randall watched, delighted.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyoin\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has her Paris itinerary all planned.\\u00c2 After Paris, Thomas hopes to compete in Los Angeles in 2028, and that's all fine with her mom.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9969016885049966, \"rank\": 0.003107940863609571, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9969016885049966, \"rank\": 0.003107940863609571, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0958299188263088e-23, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"her mom\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Great, even.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But then that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s enough of that.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI mean, come on!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Randall laments.\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"on!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Randall laments\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe has to get a Ph.D.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"a Ph.D.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t even understand why she argues with me about this.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been obvious from the beginning.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll come to realize that I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m absolutely right.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve been right about all things, by the way.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The 27-year-old Thomas, a bit of her preteen self peeking through, groans and laughs.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all things\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"the way.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"her preteen\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"groans\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"laughs\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s her biggest goal in life right now,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her biggest goal\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Randall, a professor of education at Michigan, has spent nearly three decades instilling in Thomas and her twin brother, Andrew, an artist, that they can do and be anything they want to be.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Michigan\", \"score\": 0.9999999998753992, \"rank\": 1.2291829906740652e-10, \"text\": \"Michigan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Michigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Michigan\"}, {\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Randall\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"a professor\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly three decades\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"her twin brother\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"Andrew\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"an artist\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What Gabby Thomas wants to be is the president of a hospital.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999417923, \"rank\": 5.823537400570362e-11, \"text\": \"Gabby Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"a hospital\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But first she has to finish getting what her mother callslife experience: that is, trying to win Olympic gold.\\u00c2 These days, when Thomas thinks about beinggood enough, she is generally referring to the weights she lifts, to the rest she gets, to the times she runs.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"beinggood\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"the weights\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"the times\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she tends to pass every test she gives herself: In 2023, she took silver at the world championships in the 200 meters and gold in the 4x100.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every test\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 meters\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, she won the Olympic trials in the 200 meters in 21.81 seconds, nearly a tenth of a second ahead of second place.\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 meters\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"21.81 seconds\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly a tenth\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"second place\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for a long time, she asked that question about herself as a person.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think that I have consistently been in uncomfortable situations where I had to rise to the occasion or rise to the environment that I was in,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"that question\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"uncomfortable situations\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe moved around quite a bit when I was younger, so I was kind of forced to be uncomfortable for a little bit and then make it work.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making new friends, developing new relationships, proving that I belonged in that space.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new friends\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"new relationships\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"that space\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also comes with being a young Black girl, being in very predominantly white environments, and feeling like I needed to prove that I belonged in those environments and I wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t that different, and that I was smart enough, that I was pretty enough, that I was good enough.\\\"\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young Black girl\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"very predominantly white environments\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"those environments\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas attended The Williston Northampton School, a private boarding high school in Easthampton, Mass., before enrolling at Harvard.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2809, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 2829, \"end\": 2857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Williston_Northampton_School\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Williston Northampton School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Williston_Northampton_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Williston_Northampton_School\"}, {\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shobdon\", \"score\": 0.9999999974143066, \"rank\": 2.220101765091114e-09, \"text\": \"Easthampton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shobdon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shobdon\"}, {\"begin\": 2906, \"end\": 2910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mass_in_the_Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9258762632696423, \"rank\": 0.08005543064322819, \"text\": \"Mass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mass_in_the_Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mass_in_the_Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2933, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\", \"score\": 0.9977699281003465, \"rank\": 0.0022350543514604573, \"text\": \"Harvard\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a private boarding high school\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She says she felt like she had to prove she belonged in both environments.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both environments\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had to tell myself and really believe in my heart that I did belong,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I decided to study neurobiology, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m in classes with people who\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094I can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t even tell you how insanely smart and ingenious those people are, but I just sat in those classes and contributed and asked questions, and I had to believe that I wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t asking stupid questions, or else I wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t going to make it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Early her freshman year, she found herself failing LS1B, introduction to internal life sciences.\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"neurobiology\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3137}, {\"ngram\": \"classes\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3155}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"those people\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3243}, {\"ngram\": \"those classes\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"stupid questions\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"introduction\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3490}, {\"ngram\": \"internal life sciences\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was actually failing,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNot like that cute \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098failing,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 where people are like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Haha!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 Like, I was gonna drop the class.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d If she did, she would either need to repeat the semester or choose a major other than neurobiology.\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that cute \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098failing\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"the class.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3667}, {\"ngram\": \"the semester\", \"from\": 3712, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"neurobiology\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the professor convinced her she could do it and worked with her to make a plan.\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the professor\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"a plan\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She graduated on time with that degree.\\u00c2 At times she felt the same way about track, which she initially ran because she was good at it and it was fun.\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 4004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3873}, {\"ngram\": \"that degree\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3892}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"the same way\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But by the summer after her sophomore year at Harvard, she was about ready to be done with it.\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4051, \"end\": 4058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\", \"score\": 0.9977699281003465, \"rank\": 0.0022350543514604573, \"text\": \"Harvard\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harvard_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4022}, {\"ngram\": \"her sophomore year\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wanted to focus more on studying global health.\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"global health\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the more she learned about other people\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lives, the easier hers seemed.\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other people\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lives\", \"from\": 4183, \"to\": 4205}, {\"ngram\": \"the easier hers\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She also used her mother\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s experience as a yardstick: Randall grew up as one of nine children in a two-bedroom house, the electricity out most days, and put herself through school with waitressing and teaching jobs, before raising Gabby and Andrew as a single mom.\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4288, \"end\": 4295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mother\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s experience\", \"from\": 4246, \"to\": 4271}, {\"ngram\": \"a yardstick\", \"from\": 4275, \"to\": 4286}, {\"ngram\": \"nine children\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4327}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-bedroom house\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4350}, {\"ngram\": \"the electricity\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4367}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4413}, {\"ngram\": \"waitressing\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4430}, {\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 4444, \"to\": 4448}, {\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 4465, \"to\": 4470}, {\"ngram\": \"Andrew\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4481}, {\"ngram\": \"a single mom\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI remember thinking, if she could do that, then whatever I was doing was not hard,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Thomas says.)\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4588, \"end\": 4594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4503}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She stuck with track, and\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094after agreeing with Randall that she would choose an elite running program near a school with an elite public health master\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s program\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094moved to Austin, Texas.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was not even close to being an Olympian myself,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut I forced myself to go train with them, and I forced myself to get my butt kicked in practice every day for two years, so that when the time came, I was ready to make the Olympic team.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d This is the attitude her mother always hoped to instill in her.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis is what I hope,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Randall.\", \"from\": 4602, \"to\": 5161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4650, \"end\": 4657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}, {\"begin\": 4777, \"end\": 4783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\", \"score\": 0.9992352613263247, \"rank\": 0.0007630461462799008, \"text\": \"Austin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\"}, {\"begin\": 4830, \"end\": 4838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999995652615, \"rank\": 4.350889357310454e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 5153, \"end\": 5160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4622}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite running program\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4704}, {\"ngram\": \"a school\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4718}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite public health\", \"from\": 4724, \"to\": 4746}, {\"ngram\": \"Texas\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4790}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4797}, {\"ngram\": \"my butt\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 4939}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 4958}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 4973, \"to\": 4982}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4997, \"to\": 5005}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5052}, {\"ngram\": \"the attitude\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5073}, {\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 5074, \"to\": 5084}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis\", \"from\": 5116, \"to\": 5125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou know, we always try to work out our stuff on our kids.\", \"from\": 5162, \"to\": 5223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\", \"from\": 5162, \"to\": 5168}, {\"ngram\": \"our stuff\", \"from\": 5201, \"to\": 5210}, {\"ngram\": \"our kids\", \"from\": 5214, \"to\": 5222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I absolutely feel that way, and I have always felt that way, that I wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t good enough to be in different types of spaces.\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different types\", \"from\": 5326, \"to\": 5341}, {\"ngram\": \"spaces\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think many of the spaces that Gabby walks into are remarkably elite spaces.\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the spaces\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5383}, {\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 5389, \"to\": 5394}, {\"ngram\": \"elite spaces\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think many Black women suffer with this term that I hate, but it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s real: imposter syndrome.\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many Black women\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"this term\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5485}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5503, \"to\": 5509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think what I wanted for Gabby was to not have that, to know that she was always smart, to know that she was always talented and gorgeous and all of these things.\", \"from\": 5535, \"to\": 5702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 5565, \"to\": 5570}, {\"ngram\": \"these things\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the world tells her differently all the time, right?\", \"from\": 5703, \"to\": 5759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5707, \"to\": 5716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world especially tells Black women all the time that this space does not belong to you.\", \"from\": 5760, \"to\": 5851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world\", \"from\": 5760, \"to\": 5769}, {\"ngram\": \"Black women\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5798}, {\"ngram\": \"this space\", \"from\": 5817, \"to\": 5827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And her mom couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t undo the world.\", \"from\": 5852, \"to\": 5890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mom\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5863}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5880, \"to\": 5889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s great about Gabby is that she walks into the spaces anyway, and that I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m proud of.\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5895, \"to\": 5903}, {\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 5916, \"to\": 5921}, {\"ngram\": \"the spaces\", \"from\": 5945, \"to\": 5955}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 5978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, at least I taught her to do that: Even when you feel like you don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t belong there, show up and show out.\", \"from\": 5989, \"to\": 6102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what she does, every single time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Says Thomas, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt is really hard.\", \"from\": 6103, \"to\": 6188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6159, \"end\": 6165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every single time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6131, \"to\": 6152}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 6166, \"to\": 6171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there are definitely days where you think you don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to do it.\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 6214, \"to\": 6218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are so many days where I wanted to quit, but you just do it.\", \"from\": 6262, \"to\": 6328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many days\", \"from\": 6272, \"to\": 6284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each day, you make a decision that you belong there.\", \"from\": 6329, \"to\": 6381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 6348, \"to\": 6358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And eventually you do.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Her challenge now is that everyone else knows she belongs, too.\", \"from\": 6382, \"to\": 6472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her challenge\", \"from\": 6408, \"to\": 6421}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 6434, \"to\": 6442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, she raced at Olympic Trials not expecting to make the team.\", \"from\": 6473, \"to\": 6541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"from\": 6495, \"to\": 6509}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 6532, \"to\": 6540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She ran a 21.61 200-meter race, then the third-fastest time ever recorded.\", \"from\": 6542, \"to\": 6616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 21.61 200-meter race\", \"from\": 6550, \"to\": 6572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI am still in shock,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said afterward.\", \"from\": 6617, \"to\": 6664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 6618, \"to\": 6622}, {\"ngram\": \"shock\", \"from\": 6635, \"to\": 6640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI cannot believe I put up that time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d) In Tokyo, she wandered joyfully around the Olympic Village, just trying to soak it all in.\", \"from\": 6665, \"to\": 6799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6712, \"end\": 6717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9993782748451164, \"rank\": 0.0006221114512433989, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 6665, \"to\": 6669}, {\"ngram\": \"that time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6694, \"to\": 6707}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 6748, \"to\": 6767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She came home with those two medals.\", \"from\": 6800, \"to\": 6836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those two medals\", \"from\": 6819, \"to\": 6835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Randall gave her about 30 seconds to celebrate before mentioning her fall semester at the University of Texas.)\", \"from\": 6837, \"to\": 6949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6838, \"end\": 6845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"score\": 0.9999994255787727, \"rank\": 5.74017724574379e-07, \"text\": \"Randall\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randall_Amplifiers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 30 seconds\", \"from\": 6855, \"to\": 6871}, {\"ngram\": \"her fall semester\", \"from\": 6903, \"to\": 6920}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 6924, \"to\": 6938}, {\"ngram\": \"Texas\", \"from\": 6942, \"to\": 6947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, Thomas felt set to improve upon her Tokyo performance at the world championships, but she sustained a Grade 2 strain of her right hamstring in a training run two weeks before trials.\", \"from\": 6951, \"to\": 7142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6960, \"end\": 6966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9139465996787446, \"rank\": 0.07787217291018682, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 6996, \"end\": 7001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9993782748451164, \"rank\": 0.0006221114512433989, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 7017, \"to\": 7040}, {\"ngram\": \"a Grade 2 strain\", \"from\": 7060, \"to\": 7076}, {\"ngram\": \"her right hamstring\", \"from\": 7080, \"to\": 7099}, {\"ngram\": \"a training run\", \"from\": 7103, \"to\": 7117}, {\"ngram\": \"trials\", \"from\": 7135, \"to\": 7141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She studied peer-reviewed literature and decided that daily three-hour sessions in a hyperbaric chamber would provide her best chance of healing in time.\", \"from\": 7143, \"to\": 7296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"peer-reviewed literature\", \"from\": 7155, \"to\": 7179}, {\"ngram\": \"daily three-hour sessions\", \"from\": 7197, \"to\": 7222}, {\"ngram\": \"a hyperbaric chamber\", \"from\": 7226, \"to\": 7246}, {\"ngram\": \"her best chance\", \"from\": 7261, \"to\": 7276}, {\"ngram\": \"healing\", \"from\": 7280, \"to\": 7287}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 7291, \"to\": 7295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She recovered enough to make the finals at trials, but she finished eighth and did not qualify for worlds.\", \"from\": 7297, \"to\": 7403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 7326, \"to\": 7336}, {\"ngram\": \"trials\", \"from\": 7340, \"to\": 7346}, {\"ngram\": \"worlds\", \"from\": 7396, \"to\": 7402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She was named to the team as a possibility on the relay squad, but the coaches did not use her.)\", \"from\": 7404, \"to\": 7501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 7422, \"to\": 7430}, {\"ngram\": \"a possibility\", \"from\": 7434, \"to\": 7447}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay squad\", \"from\": 7451, \"to\": 7466}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 7472, \"to\": 7483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was crushed.\", \"from\": 7502, \"to\": 7518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, she believes that the time off helped her focus on the journey, which is perspective she needs now that she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not an underdog anymore.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cGoing into Tokyo, no one really believed in me, which made it a little bit easier,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 7519, \"to\": 7763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7679, \"end\": 7684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9993782748451164, \"rank\": 0.0006221114512433989, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 7544, \"to\": 7552}, {\"ngram\": \"the journey\", \"from\": 7577, \"to\": 7588}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 7599, \"to\": 7610}, {\"ngram\": \"an underdog\", \"from\": 7642, \"to\": 7653}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 7685, \"to\": 7691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was really just about my journey and having fun.\", \"from\": 7764, \"to\": 7818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 7764, \"to\": 7769}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 7792, \"to\": 7802}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 7814, \"to\": 7817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s all upside.\", \"from\": 7819, \"to\": 7837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 7819, \"to\": 7825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now the gold is really mine to lose, and every time I step on the track, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s my race to lose.\", \"from\": 7838, \"to\": 7938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 7846, \"to\": 7854}, {\"ngram\": \"every time\", \"from\": 7883, \"to\": 7893}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 7904, \"to\": 7913}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 7915, \"to\": 7921}, {\"ngram\": \"my race\", \"from\": 7922, \"to\": 7929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So you definitely have to have another reason for competing other than just winning.\", \"from\": 7939, \"to\": 8023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another reason\", \"from\": 7970, \"to\": 7984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Winning cannot be your end all, be all to sport.\", \"from\": 8024, \"to\": 8072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your end\", \"from\": 8042, \"to\": 8050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It cannot be your reason to exist or reason to be.\", \"from\": 8073, \"to\": 8123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your reason\", \"from\": 8086, \"to\": 8097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So for me, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s about just being my best self.\", \"from\": 8124, \"to\": 8172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best self\", \"from\": 8159, \"to\": 8171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s about showcasing what you can do.\", \"from\": 8173, \"to\": 8213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 8173, \"to\": 8179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I know that there are a lot of people watching, especially the younger generation, and other girls who are watching us compete the same way that I did growing up.\", \"from\": 8214, \"to\": 8380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 8240, \"to\": 8245}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 8249, \"to\": 8255}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the younger generation\", \"from\": 8266, \"to\": 8299}, {\"ngram\": \"other girls\", \"from\": 8305, \"to\": 8316}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8334, \"to\": 8336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s: How can I be a great role model for them?\", \"from\": 8381, \"to\": 8437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great role model\", \"from\": 8409, \"to\": 8427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How can I be an example for them?\", \"from\": 8438, \"to\": 8471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 8451, \"to\": 8461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What do I want to leave the sport?\\u00e2\